.TH LOA-DETAILS 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
details \- Show one item in a structured detail view
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> details
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for an item reference.
.TP
References can be ID, ISBN, or fuzzy text matching title/author/composer.
.TP
Displays all relevant fields in a readable section layout.
.TP
Includes shared metadata plus sheet-music fields (composer, instrumentation, catalog, key, practice) when applicable.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> details
.TP
alexandria> (enter: b0001)
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-check(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Generated for the Library Of Alexandria project.
